data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the serene and sought-after community! This 4-bedroom Huntington model home constructed in 2023 by Maronda Homes boasts a bonus den/office, 3 bathrooms, and exquisite architectural details, a testament to modern luxury and comfort. *BETTER THAN NEW with reverse osmosis water treatment and new Samsung Refrigerator added by seller. *BEDROOMS: Features 4 bedrooms with space for family and guests plus a bonus den/office to customize for your needs. *BATHROOMS: 3 well-appointed bathrooms, each designed with convenience and style in mind. *ELEGANCE EVERYWHERE: crown molding and unique ceiling trays, for a touch of sophistication. *EXPANSIVE LIVING SPACE: 2,286 SF to spread out and make this home uniquely your own. *OUTDOOR BLISS: extra-large screened lanai with half an acre. Room for a pool or create your own outdoor oasis for entertaining or relaxation. *TRANQUIL SETTING: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, own a piece of PARADISE. Schedule your private tour today and experience the blend of luxury, comfort, and space that this home offers. Your new beginning awaits in this stunning Maronda Homes masterpiece!
